(2000001483,'Stripping energy from our foes, both fighting and fallen, allows us to persevere where lesser beings fall exhausted.',0,0,0,0,NULL),
(2000001484,'And every foe that falls, energy sapped and stolen, only furthers our assault.',0,0,0,0,NULL),
(2000001485,'As masters of blood, we know battle without end...',0,0,0,0,NULL),
(2000001486,'We know hunger never to be quenched...',0,0,0,0,NULL),
(2000001487,'We know power never to be overcome...',0,0,0,0,NULL),
